Great Stasis
Discworld ritual help
Great Stasis

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Great stasis - Traps your targets in crystal spheres.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This offensive ritual is used to ask your god to trap everyone in
the room with you into small, individual, prison-like crystal
spheres for a short time.  You will need a prayer book and some
incense to perform this.
.EP
